<doc id="1099143" wikidata="Q932536" url="?curid=1099143" title="Every Man a Tiger">
<text>Every Man a Tiger (1999) is Tom Clancy&#x27;s second book in his &quot;Study in Command&quot; series. It is partially a biography of General Chuck Horner (CENTAF during Operation Desert Storm and Desert Shield), but mostly it is a study of the command decisions, preparations, and execution of air war of Operation Desert Storm.

The book is mostly written by Tom Clancy with sections where he uses General Horner&#x27;s own words.

